@itdependsnetworks You can't update `reverse_mapping` as that is modifying the original dictionary and will potentially have unintended behavior if multiple calls are made.

You will need to do something like:

```
name_map_reverse = {}
name_map_reverse.update(reverse_mapping)

# Then...
    if isinstance(addl_reverse_map, dict):
         name_map_reverse.update(addl_reverse_map)

# And update additional references to use name_map_reverse
```
